answers.answer: What were you FT-3 and TSH levels??

question: My FT4 Dialysis is 0.9 and my military Doctor told me that he does not know why.  I am not over weight and I do not have Diabetes.  I am on testosterone gel (2.5 Grams) and my total count was 220 and my Testos free was 63.6.   Any help  on what I should do?
title: Low FT4
